YSh Ur'yH 'aShUr Ur'aYThY ThChTh HShMSh VUrBH HY'a 'yL-H'aDM.
'aYSh 'aShUr YThN-LV H'aLHYM 'yShUr VNKSYM VKBVD V'aYNNV ChSUr LNPhShV MKL 'aShUr-YTh'aVH VL'a-YShLYTNV H'aLHYM L'aKL MMNV KY 'aYSh NKUrY Y'aKLNV ZH HBL VChLY Ur'y HV'a.
'aM-YVLYD 'aYSh M'aH VShNYM UrBVTh YChYH VUrB ShYHYV YMY-ShNYV VNPhShV L'a- ThShB'y MN-HTVBH VGM-QBVUrH L'a-HYThH LV 'aMUrThY TVB MMNV HNPhL.
KY-BHBL B'a VBChShK YLK VBChShK ShMV YKSH.
GM-ShMSh L'a-Ur'aH VL'a YD'y NChTh LZH MZH.
V'aLV ChYH 'aLPh ShNYM Ph'yMYM VTVBH L'a Ur'aH HL'a 'aL-MQVM 'aChD HKL HVLK.
KL-'yML H'aDM LPhYHV VGM-HNPhSh L'a ThML'a.
KY MH-YVThUr LChKM MN-HKSYL MH-L'yNY YVD'y LHLK NGD HChYYM.
TVB MUr'aH 'yYNYM MHLK-NPhSh GM-ZH HBL VUr'yVTh UrVCh.
MH-ShHYH KBUr NQUr'a ShMV VNVD'y 'aShUr-HV'a 'aDM VL'a-YVKL LDYN 'yM ShHThQYPh MMNV.
KY YSh-DBUrYM HUrBH MUrBYM HBL MH-YThUr L'aDM.
KY MY-YVD'y MH-TVB L'aDM BChYYM MSPhUr YMY-ChYY HBLV VY'yShM KTShL 'aShUr MY-YGYD L'aDM MH-YHYH 'aChUrYV ThChTh HShMSh.
